               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary>A composite manuscript containing:  
<list>
  <item>An incomplete copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Varākimālai</title> (1 unnumbered stanza + 6 numbered stanzas) (Indien 9a).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Cauntariyalakari</title> (Indien 9b).</item>
  <item>A <foreign xml:lang="ta">cakkaram</foreign> with <foreign xml:lang="ta">mantiram</foreign>s (Indien 9c). According to the title page folio (U1), this the <foreign xml:lang="ta">cakkaram</foreign> of the <title xml:lang="ta">Cauntariyalakari</title>.</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Niṭṭāṉupūtiviḷakkam</title> (Indien 9d).</item>
  <item>TBC (Indien 9e).</item>
  <item>TBC (Indien 9f).</item>
  </list>
These are preceded by an additional title page folio (U1) listing four works contianed in the bundle.</summary>
                  
                  
